        "formula": "设 G = num_groups, C = 8192, Cg = C // G = 512。将 linear_out 重塑为 (N, G, Cg) 视图：X3[n, g, r] = linear_out[n, g*Cg + r]。对 n in [0,N), g in [0,G): mu[n,g] = (1/Cg) * sum_{r=0}^{Cg-1} X3[n,g,r]; var[n,g] = (1/Cg) * sum_{r=0}^{Cg-1} (X3[n,g,r] - mu[n,g])^2。则 group_norm_out[n, g*Cg + c] = gamma[g*Cg + c] * (X3[n,g,c] - mu[n,g]) / sqrt(var[n,g] + eps) + beta[g*Cg + c]。",
